0/torrijos-town-resident-is-marinduques-first-covid-19-case |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=March 23, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**[[Occidental Mindoro]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Virola |first1=Madonna |title=Deceased man is 1st COVID-19 case of Occidental Mindoro |url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1249506/deceased-woman-is-1st-covid-19-case-of-occidental-mindoro |accessdate=March 30, 2020 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=March 27, 2020}}</ref>\n**[[Oriental Mindoro]]<ref name=\"surges\"/>\n<!---No cases yet in Palawan outside Puerto Princessa--->\n**''[[Puerto Princesa]]''<ref name=\"Inquirer-CovidPalawan\">{{cite news |last1=Miranda |first1=Romar |title=Palawan records first COVID-19 case |url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1246013/palawan-records-first-covid-19-case |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=March 21, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n*[[Bicol Region]] (Region V)\n**[[Albay]]<ref name=bicolfirst>{{cite news |title=Bicol region records first cases of COVID-19 |url=https://www.cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/3/27/bicol-coronavirus.html |accessdate=March 30, 2020 |work=CNN Philippines |date=March 27, 2020}}</ref>\n**[[Camarines Sur]]<ref name=\"Inquirer-CovidBicol\">{{cite news |last1=Arguelles |first1=Mar S. |title=Bicol records 4th COVID-19 positive case |url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1250150/bicol-records-4th-covid-19-positive-case |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=March 28, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**''[[Naga City, Camarines Sur|Naga]]''<ref name=bicolfirst/>\n*[[Western Visayas]] (Region VI)\n**[[Aklan]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidWestVisayas\">{{cite news |last1=Momblan |first1=Gail |title=W. Visayas confirms 9 new Covid-19 cases |url=https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1098069 |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine News Agency |date=March 27, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**''[[Bacolod]]''<ref name=\"PIAGovPH-CovidBacolod\">{{cite news |last1=Lambatin |first1=